  "name": "Striking Stance Python",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Hebi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can only gain the benefit from one Striking Stance at a time. If you enter another Striking Stance while currently benefiting from this one, the one immediately ends.</p><p> You enter the striking stance of a python. For the duration, creatures gaining a bonus to their AC as a result of a jutsu, feature or trait and structures summoned as a result of a jutsu, feature or trait intended to intercept damage dealt become Vulnerable to the first Taijutsu Attack you make using a component weapon on your turn.</p>",
